Il y a 300 millions dannes, il tait
craint comme lultime prdateur. Il a
t modifi par la Team Plasma.

Over 300 million years ago, it was feared
as the strongest of hunters.
It has been modified by Team Plasma.

Un Pokmon Insecte des temps anciens
modifi par la Team Plasma. Le canon
dans son dos a t grandement amlior.

This ancient bug Pokmon was altered
by Team Plasma. They upgraded the
cannon on its back.

This Pokmon existed 300 million years
ago. Team Plasma altered it and
attached a cannon to its back.
